                            <item xml:id="a1">
                              <locus target="#40v">Fol. 40v</locus>
                              <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership or purchase note, almost completely erased. Only the incipit is readable: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ</foreign>፡. The following words are also readable on the next line: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአጥረዮ፡</foreign></desc>
                              
